Here are the authoritative public test cases for feature1_3_read_path:
{
  "description": "Safely read a value from a nested object by walking an ordered path of keys. Empty path segments (empty string, null, undefined) are skipped rather than dereferenced. A path that does not exist yields no value (null).",
  "cases": [
    {
      "input": {
        "op": "read_path",
        "object": {
